        <body>
            
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:83215">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi>
                </ab>
                <p>	
                    kō-māṟa-paṉmar-āṉa tiri-puvaṉa-c-cakkara-va<reg>r</reg>ttikaḷ cōṇāṭu ko(ṇṭ-a)
                    <lb n="2" break="no"/>ruḷiya <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>-cuntara-pāṇṭiya-tēvaṟku yāṇṭu 3-vatu
                </p>
                <p>
                    tiru-malai-nāṭṭu-t tiru-k-koṭuṅ
                    <lb n="3" break="no"/>-kuṉṟattu Uṭaiyār tiru-k-koṭuṅ-kuṉṟam-uṭaiya nāyaṉāṟku ka <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character" precision="low"/> valil paratēci A
                    <lb n="4" break="no"/>ṇṭārkaḷil tiru-naṭṭa-p-perumāḷ piḷḷaikaḷil Etir-illā-p perumāḷ <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character" precision="low"/> ceyam-uṭaiya peru
                    <lb n="5" break="no"/>māḷ-āṉa tiru-nīṟu pēṇi yaṇivāṉēṉ cantirātitta-vaṟ celvat' āka tiru-ṉuntā-viḷakku Oṉ
                    <lb n="6" break="no"/>ṟukku (cāvā mūvā-p) pēr-āṭ' āka-k koṇṭu viṭṭa Āṭu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character" precision="low"/>
                </p>
                <p>Inta viḷakk' eriya Iṭṭa pittaḷai viḷakku Oṉ
                    <lb n="7" break="no"/>ṟināl Iṭai <num value="72">7 <g type="numeral">10</g> 2</num> palamum Iv-āṭu Am-patum koṇṭu kalveṭṭi-k kuṭuttōm tiru-nīṟu pēṇi Aṇi
                    <lb n="8"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character" precision="low"/>		
                </p>
